Company Overview of kWantera, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
kWantera, Inc. provides a platform that gives end users daily and hourly visibility into the price of energy and provides customized bid and offer recommendations for buyers and sellers. The company combines data analytics technologies with its lineage of machine learning and pattern-recognition technologies, producing a customizable, cloud-based platform for buyers and sellers in energy market. kWantera, Inc. was formerly known as MobileFusion, Inc. and changed its name to kWantera, Inc. in February 2012. kWantera, Inc. was founded in 2006 and is based in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania.


2740 Smallman StreetSuite 401Pittsburgh, PA 15222United StatesFounded in 2006



