kWantera, Inc. Key Developments

kWantera, Inc. Presents at 19th Annual Needham Growth Conference, Jan-11-2017 11:00 AM
Dec 13 16
kWantera, Inc. Presents at 19th Annual Needham Growth Conference, Jan-11-2017 11:00 AM. Venue: Lotte New York Palace, 455 Madison Avenue at 50th Stree, New York, NY 10022, United States.


kWantera to Form Technology Alliance with GE Renewable Energy
Oct 4 16
kWantera and General Electric Company, through its GE Renewable Energy business announced a technology alliance to offer kWantera’s energy trading solution to complement GE’s Digital Wind Farm offering. GE Renewable Energy is developing a partner network and engaging the start-up ecosystem to enhance its Digital Wind Farm and other digital products on its Predix platform. This alliance will enable both kWantera and GE Renewable Energy to co-develop digital solutions that allow renewable energy customers to better manage operational risk and scheduling decisions, thereby enhancing revenue from their asset base.


kWantera, Inc. Appoints Jon Wellinghoff to its Board
Feb 10 16
Jon Wellinghoff has joined the board of kWantera Inc., his first board appointment since stepping down as chairman of the Federal Energy Regulation Commission in 2013. Based in the Strip District, kWantera uses advanced predictive analytics to identify the best price, time and location at which to purchase, sell or consume power in deregulated markets.


