Decision Intelligence for Energy Markets
Energy decisions are complex, especially in a deregulated market where
                        opportunities are abundant but insight is scarce. With Faraday, you can now
                        navigate the vast amounts of data available - curated into digestible and
                        actionable recommendations to guide your energy strategy.
                    




Request a Free Trial








 Faraday: Energy's Smartest Platform








                        We've created Faraday, an energy intelligence platform that specializes in advanced
                        data science and predictive analytics for the energy markets. Faraday tackles a number of
                        common market challenges, as well as constraint-based problems, for both buyers and sellers
                        of power.
                    
 With Faraday you can:

Control and reduce price-risk in your indexed or fixed rate energy spend
Manage capacity and demand charges with proactive consumption avoidance
Improve offer and bid strategies to increase profitability
Optimally deploy distributed generation and storage assets through market signals
Gain visibility to energy market features- pricing, load, fees, structural flows, etc.
Enhance and support your power trading activities





