                Banking & Financial Services            


DeSantis apparently out at kWantera




Mar 4, 2016, 11:28am EST






Industries & Tags


                    Banking & Financial Services,                 



                    Career & Workplace,                 



                    Energy,                 


            Executive Profiles,              

            Software             














Patty Tascarella


Senior Reporter
Pittsburgh Business Times













