Short description




We are changing the way companies approach the energy industry, using advanced data science and predictive analytics. In today's complex and unpredictable power markets, participants are presented with unique challenges. Faraday, our energy intelligence platform, provides actionable insights and increases efficiency in the decision-making process. Whether participants are looking to reduce energy costs, tap into ancillary market opportunities or improve revenue yield, Faraday supplies data-driven recommendations for optimizing energy strategies...
 We've created Faraday, an energy intelligence platform that specializes in advanced data science and predictive analytics for the energy markets. Faraday tackles a number of common market challenges, as well as constraint-based problems, for both buyers and sellers of power.














